title: Coocaa 81 cm (32 inch) HD Ready LED Smart TV with YouTube  (32S3U)

product_specification.In The Box: 1N LED TV, 1N WALLMOUNT, 1N REMOTE, 2N BATTERIES, 1N BASE STAND INSTALLATION, 2N BASE STAND, 2N SCREWS, 1N USER MANUAL, 1N WARRANTY CARD.
product_specification.Other Video Features: Built-in Digital Media, Digital Audio Output to Connect External Audio Systems
product_specification.Other Audio Features: Automatic Volume Level (AVL), Digital Media Player (DMP) Content: Music, Music Alone mode, Audio Equalizer
product_specification.Graphic User Interface: Penta Core ARM Mali 450 MP Upto 750 MHz
product_specification.Other Internet Features: EROS NOW/ Hungama/Watch N/ Youtube/Toon goggles/Radioline/Deezer/WeatherNation
product_specification.Stand Type: Wall Mount and Table Top Stand
product_specification.Covered in Warranty: Warranty of the Product is Limited to Manufacturing Defects Only
product_specification.Not Covered in Warranty: Warranty Does Not Cover Any External Accessories (Such as Battery, Cable, Carrying Bag), Damage Caused to the Product Due to Improper Installation by Customer, Normal Wear and Tear to Magnetic Heads, Audio, Video, Laser Pick-ups and TV Picture Tubes, Panel, Damages Caused to the Product by Accident, Lightening, Ingress of Water, Fire, Dropping or Excessive Shock, Any Damage Caused Due to Tampering of the Product by an Unauthorized Agent, Liability for Loss of Data, Recorded Images or Business Opportunity Loss.
product_specification.Installation & Demo Details: 1. Covered Under Standard Installation - Table Mounting Using Standard Stand Supplied as Accessory with TV - Extra Charges are Applicable for Wall Mounts as, Rs. 399 for 32 inch Display Size and Rs. 499 for >32 inch Display Size - Connecting with Available Power Source (within 1 Meter) - Connecting / Setting Up Various Available Input Source for Audio Video Based on Model - Connecting with Available WiFi (for Smart TV) - Checking TV for Proper Functioning - Demonstration of the TV and its Features

product_description.Stylish Build: This stylish and modish TV from Coocaa adds an aesthetic appeal to your modern home interiors. The almost frameless design of this TV takes its style quotient up by a notch.
product_description.Trochilus Extreme Picture Engine: The Trochilus Extreme Picture Engine technology of this TV offers a stunning viewing experience as it automatically adjusts the dynamic contrast, skin color, and true color restoration. So, even if you’re watching a music video, a movie, or a TV series on this appliance, you will view every detail and rich and vivid colors.
